e=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">384-wells</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">板进行快速定量及定量分析</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">功能用途：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">可用于</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">DNA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">RNA</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">、蛋白质的吸收光定量检测，酶动力学检测（乙酰胆碱酯酶、乳酸脱氢酶等），酶活性相关分析（激酶、蛋白酶），光谱分析、凝集分析及比色分析，食品和环境监测。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;ma