top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器简介：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">海能</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">SOX500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">脂肪测定仪是根据索氏抽提原理，采用重量法来测定脂肪含量的全自动粗脂肪测定仪。仪器具有索氏标准法（国标法）、索氏热萃取、热萃取、连</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">续流动及</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">CH</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">标准热萃取等五种萃取方式；可自动实现萃取、淋洗、溶剂回收和预干燥四大功能；海能</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">SOX500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">脂肪测定仪采用一体式金属浴加热，升温效果更加完善；彩色触摸显示屏及其简约的界面设计风格给人全新感受；采用外置操作面板；内置乙醚泄漏检测装置有效防止空气污染，充分保障了实验的安全性。海能</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">SOX500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">脂肪测定仪广泛应用于农业、食品、环境及工业等不同的领域，是食品、油料、饲料等行业脂肪测定的理想仪器；也可应用于药品、土壤、污泥、清洁</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">剂等物质中的可溶性有机化合物的萃取。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">功能用途：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">可用于动物组织、植物组织、饲料等脂肪含量的测定，也可应用于药物、土壤、污泥等物质中的可溶性有机化合物的萃取或测定。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height: 150%;font-family:宋体\">氨基酸分析仪</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><img src=\"/Upload/image/20161116/6361489762878192677427039.jpg\" hspace=\"12\" title=\"clip_image053.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器型号</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">S 433D</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;text-indent:0;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">生产厂家</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：德国赛卡姆公司</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;text-indent:0;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">购置年份</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">存放地点：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">重点实验室</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">408</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器简介：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0 10px 28px;text-indent: 28px;line-height: 150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">S-433D</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">采用的树脂柱是一种特殊的离子交换材料，与每种氨基酸有不同反应，当不同的缓冲液进入分离柱时，因溶液的</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">PH</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">值、离子强度、分离柱温度以及各</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">种氨基酸本身的性质不同而使各种氨基酸得以分离，分离后的氨基酸与茚三酮试剂在高温反应器中发生衍生反应，生成可以被分光光度计检测的有色物质，仪器通过</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">精确控制各种分离条件以保证定性定量检测的重复性。</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\"> S-433D</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">型氨基酸分析仪由四个单元组成：带电子冷却装置及惰性气体保护的溶液存放单元</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">S7130</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、四元梯度泵</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">S2100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（输液单元）、带电子恒温的自</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">动进样器</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">S5200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、氨基酸反应单元</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">S4300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（分离、检测单元）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">功能用途：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0 10px 28px;text-indent: 28px;line-height: 150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">可用于测定饲料、农作物中的氨基酸含量。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0 10px 28px;text-indent: 28px;line-height: 150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0 10px 28px;text-indent: 28px;line-height: 150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0 10px 28px;text-indent: 28px;line-height: 150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0 10px 28px;text-indent: 28px;line-height: 150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0 10px 28px;text-indent: 28px;line-height: 150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height: 150%;font-family:宋体\">双色红外激光成像系统</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;line-height:150%\"><img src=\"/Upload/image/20161116/6361489762883146473412947.jpg\" hspace=\"12\" title=\"clip_image054.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器型号</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Odyssey clx</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;text-indent:0;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">生产厂家</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：美国</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">LI-COR</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;text-indent:0;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">购置年份</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">存放地点：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">重点实验室</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">407</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器简介：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Odyssey </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">双色红外激光成像系统是根据大分子物质在红外波长区几乎不发生任何荧光信号的特点，使得膜上检测核酸和蛋白成为可能。可用以检测膜、凝胶和微孔板上的荧光标记物。可同时进行双色检测（两个目标基因同时检测，减少了工作量，而且杂交条件均等）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">功能用途：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">利用红外染料技术对膜、凝胶、微孔板上的蛋白、核酸等检测物进行扫描成像并分析，可用于</span><span style=\"font-