f&#39;\">PCR</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">仪将</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">CFX96 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">光学系统与</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">C1000M </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">热循环仪结合起来，组成功能强大，检测灵敏的实时定量</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">PCR</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">系统。六通道的实时定量</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">PCR</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">系统包括了先进的光学系统和精确的温控系统，能使每个通道中染料达到最佳效果，对靶基因进行精确定量和分型，可提供高灵敏，可信赖的检测结果。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">功能用途：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">用于核酸的绝对定量、核算的相对定量、</span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">SNPs </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">基因型分型和带有内部阳性对照的阴</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">阳性分析。可应用于动植物基因表达分析、临床疾病诊断、动物疾病检测、食品安全等方面。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height: 150%;font-family:宋体\">全自动间断化学分析仪</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><img src=\"/Upload/image/20161116/6361489762920367572598382.jpg\" hspace=\"12\" title=\"clip_image060.jpg\"/><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:7px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器型号</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Cleverchem200+</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:7px;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">生产厂家</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：德国</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">DeChem-Tech</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:7px;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">购置年份</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:7px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">存放地点：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">重点实验室</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">403</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器简介：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:28px;margin-bottom:0;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">CleverChem200+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">全自动间断化学分析仪是将比色分析法自动化的一种分析测试手段，它完全模拟人工比色法，将样品、试剂和显色剂加入比色皿中产生颜色反应，待测物浓度与反应液最终颜色深浅成正比关系，经比色计检测透光强度，得到相应的峰值吸光度，再通过标准曲线自动计算得到相应的浓度。一次可分析多个参数的</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">119</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个样品，所有步骤通过进样臂和电脑控制，充分实现机械化和智能化。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">其性能优势包括以下几点：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">多参数同时分析，一次性可以同时测定</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">119</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个样品的多个参数；</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">一次可分析的样品量多，分析速度快，分析速度最高可达</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个样</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">小时；</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">自动化程度高，实现自动取样、自动取试剂、自动稀释超标样品、自动制作标准曲线、自动清洗比色皿、自动光学测试，除此还可实现样品量或试剂量不足的警报、清洗液不足及废液过满的警报、故障的自动分析等。</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">配置有高精度微量取样器，取样量为</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">1-400μL</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，试剂量为</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">1-450μL</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，减少了样品和试剂的消耗。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">功能用途：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">从高浓度的</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">ppm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">级到痕量的</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">ppt</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">级均可以分析。主要应用于大气、土壤和水环境中各种</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">N</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">P</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">K</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">等元素的定性定量分析。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height: 150%;font-family:宋体\">原子吸收分光光度计</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><img src=\"/Upload/image/20161116/6361489762925300257584290.jpg\" hspace=\"12\" title=\"clip_image061.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:7px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器型号</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">GGX-6</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:7px;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">生产厂家</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：北京科创公司</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:7px;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">购置年份</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2011</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:7px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">存放地点：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">重点实验室</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">401</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器简介：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">GGX-6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原子吸收分光光度计由光源、原子化系统、分光系统和检测系统组成。其基本原理是根据物质基态原子蒸汽对特征辐射吸收的作用来进行金属元素分析。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器参数如下：</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">自动程度：自动负高压、自动灯电流、自动能量调节。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">功能：火焰型塞曼背景校正。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">光路：采用</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">C-T</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">型光栅单色器，平面闪耀光栅。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">气路：气压安全监测，防回火，意外情况自动切断燃气。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">偏振器：洛匈棱镜。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:94px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">雾化系统：金属套高效玻璃雾化器，雾化效率高，提升量小，十分适合生物样品分析。钛金属燃烧头具有火焰升降、水平转角调节机构。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">信号检测：日本进口高灵敏度光电倍增管。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">工作波段：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">190-900nm</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">波长精度：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">±0.3nm</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">基线稳定性：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">0.003A/30min</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分辨率：优于</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">0.3nm</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">测量参数：从高浓度的</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">ppm</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">级到痕量的</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">ppt</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">级均可以分析。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">功能用途：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">主要应用于</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">K</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Ca</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Na</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Mg</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Cu</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Zn</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Mo</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Mn</span><span style=\"font-fami