t:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height: 150%;font-family:宋体\">碳氮分析仪</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><img src=\"/Upload/image/20161116/6361489762928738479340953.jpg\" hspace=\"12\" title=\"clip_image062.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:14px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器型号</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Vario toc6</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:14px;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">生产厂家</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：德国</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">elementar</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:14px;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">购置年份</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:14px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">存放地点：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">重点实验室</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">403</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器简介：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">与低温或湿化学法（如</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">COD</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）测量有机污染物相比较，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Elementar</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">理念提供了较多优势：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2-3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">分钟的分析时间；安全和无害环境下的操作，无高浓度酸、氧化剂和烈性化学品或有害废物；</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">％碳的回收率；不依赖样品种类、或含颗粒和含盐溶液；在分析</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">TOC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的同时分析总氮（</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">TNb</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">高分析通量；低分析成本，全自动操作。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">技术参数：</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">测量范围：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">0—60,000ppm C (in liquids)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">0—100% (in solid)</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">可实现固体</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">液体全自动进样</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">功能用途：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">适用于超纯水（医药用水），饮用水，工业废水，悬浮液甚至是极难分析的固体样品矩阵的</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">TOC/TNb</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分析。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height: 150%;font-family:宋体\">根系分析系统</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><img src=\"/Upload/image/20161116/6361489762933866105326861.jpg\" hspace=\"12\" title=\"clip_image063.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:14px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器型号</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">WinRHIZO</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:14px;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">生产厂家</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：加拿大</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Regent</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:14px;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">购置年份</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:14px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">存放地点：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">重点实验室</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">411</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器简介：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">WinRHIZO</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是一套用于洗根后的专业根系分析系统，可以分析根系长度、直径、面积、体积、根尖记数等，功能强大，操作简单，广泛运用于根系形态和构造研究。</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\"> </span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">WinRHIZO</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">利用高质量图形扫描系统提供高分辨率的彩色图像或黑白图像，该扫描系统匹配专门的双光源照明系统，去除了阴影和不均匀现象的影响，有效的保证了图像的质量。采用非统计学方法测量计算出交叉重叠部分根系长度等参量，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">WinRHIZO</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">可以读取</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">TIFF</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">JPEG</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">标准格式的图像。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:0;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">功能用途：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">测量参数：根总长、平均直径、总面积、总体积、根尖、交叉和交叠计数、不同根直径等级分布参数等。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">主要应用在根系形态、根系存活、根系营养状况、根系连接分析（分支角度、连通性）、根系拓扑分析（根系连接数量、路径长度）和根系分级伸展（记录根系整体等级分布情况）等。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">调制叶绿素荧光成像系统</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><img src=\"/Upload/image/20161116/6361489762937218101312769.jpg\" hspace=\"12\" title=\"clip_image064.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:21px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器型号</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">MINI-IMAGING-PAM</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">生产厂家</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：德国</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">WALZ</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">购置年份</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:21px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">存放地点：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">重点实验室</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">409</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:7px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器简介：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">MINI-IMAGING-PAM</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">调制叶绿素荧光成像系统，配备</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">MINI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">探头，采用强大的</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Luxeon LED</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">阵列，包括</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">组（每组</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">个）</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">LED</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">，均配有长波截止滤光片。配备</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">个红光（</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">650nm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）和</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">个近红外（</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">780nm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">LED</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">，用于测量叶片吸光系数的成像。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">测量参数：全叶片光合作用分析（荧光成像），荧光诱导曲线、快速光响应曲线和叶片吸光系数等。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:7px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">功能用途：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">应用于遗传育种的突变株筛选、叶片光合作用的横向异质性、胁迫损伤的早期检测和绿色荧光蛋白（</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">GFP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）荧光测量等。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height: 150%;font-family:宋体\">植物根系生长监测系统</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><img src=\"/Upload/image/20161116/6361489762820497307770555.jpg\" hspace=\"12\" title=\"clip_image039.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:21px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器型号</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">CI-600</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">生产厂家</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：美国</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">LI-COR</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">购置年份</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:21px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">存放地点：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">重点实验室</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">409</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:7px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:7px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:7px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:7px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器简介：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">植物根系生长监测系统</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">CI-600</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是全球第一套</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">“</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">土壤原位</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">360</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">度多层次旋转式图像监测仪</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">”</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">可以获取土壤、根系剖面图像，监测土壤中活体根系的生长动态。用户可以方便的获取同一地点不同深度的根系图像，以及不同地点不同根系的图像。每次可获得</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">21.56 x 19.56 cm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的高分辨率图像，用户可以看到根系（甚至土壤颗粒）的详细结构。专业根系分析软件分析计算根长、根面积、体积、根尖数等根系形态参数，可进行不同时间空间多幅图片的拼接，具备强大的根系形态分析功能，是研究监测根系生长，根系生理生态、根系抗逆性研究和土壤颗粒变化等的专业工具。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">CI-600 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">根系生长监测系统可以方便地非破坏性原位获取土壤中活体根系的生长动态图像数据。用户使用柱型设计的</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">360</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">度旋转光电耦合主机，获取定位的不同时间季节、不同深度的根系分布或土壤剖面图像数据。应用专业根系分析软件</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:7px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">功能用途：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">主要用于分析根系长度、直径、截面积、投影面积、根尖数等参数。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:47px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height: 150%;font-family:宋体\">便携式光合作用仪</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><img src=\"/Upload/image/20161116/6361489762942177161596849.jpg\" hspace=\"12\" title=\"clip_image065.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:21px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器型号</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">LI-6400</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">生产厂家</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：美国</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">LI-COR</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">公司</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">购置年份</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2010</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:21px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">存放地点：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">重点实验室</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">409</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:7px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器简介：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">LI-6400 XT</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">便携式光合作用测量系统是当今国际上植物叶片光合作用测量的最先进仪器。在实验过程中可以控制叶片周围的</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">CO<sub>2</sub></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">浓度、</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">H<sub>2</sub>O</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">浓度、温度、相对湿度、光照强度和叶室温度等所有相关的环境条件对植物叶片的气体交换特征进行测定。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:21px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">测量参数：净光合速率（</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Pn</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）、气孔导度（</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Gs</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）、蒸腾速率（</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Ts</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）、细胞间隙</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">CO<sub>2</sub></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">浓度（</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Ci</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）、大气</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">CO<sub>2</sub></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">浓度（</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Ca</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）、光量子通量密度（</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">PFD</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）、叶温（</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">TL</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）、气温（</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Ta</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）、相对空气湿度（</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">RH</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）、饱和蒸汽压亏缺（</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">VPD</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">），以及表观量子效率（</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">AQY</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）、羧化效率（</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">CE</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）气孔限制值（</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Ls</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）、光呼吸速率、</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">CO<sub>2</sub></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">利用率（</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">CUE</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）、总光合速率（</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Pgross</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）、暗呼吸速率等。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:7px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">功能用途：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">可用于光响应曲线、</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">CO2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">响应曲线、光合作用机理、光合作用动态变化、逆境条件植物光合作用变化等。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-align:center;text-indent:47px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height: 150%;font-family:宋体\">多参数水质监测仪</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><img src=\"/Upload/image/20161116/6361489762945329238055339.jpg\" hspace=\"12\" title=\"clip_image066.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:21px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:21px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器型号</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">YSI-6600</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">生产厂家</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：美国维赛公司</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:21px;line-height:200%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">购置年份</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:21px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">存放地点：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">重点实验室</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">409</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:7px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">仪器简介：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">YSI 6600</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是一款适用于多点采样测量、长期现场监测与剖面分析的多参数仪器，可同时监测多达</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个参数。具有</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">90</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">天电池寿命与</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">9</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">组探头结构，其中包括两个供浊度、叶绿素或罗丹明探头同时安装的光学口。操作水深达</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">米。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px;text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多参数水质检测仪体积小、功能强，适用于不同水体的多点采样、定点式数据采集、长期连续在线监测和剖面分析。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:7px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">功能用途：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">可用于测定水中溶解氧、电导率、酸碱度、盐度、浊度、铵氮</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">氨氮、硝氮、氯化物等指标。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:28px;text-indent:35px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;text-indent:7px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>', '', '0', 'jbxx', '基本信息', 'yqsb', '仪器设备', '10000', '3', '2016-11-15 00:00:00', '');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('7', '管理员', '', '实验室', '西北大学齐晓光教授来我校讲学', '<p style=\"text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">为加强学术交流与合作，</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">6</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">4</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">日下午</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">4</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">：</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">00</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">，西北大学生命科学学院副院长、博士生导师齐晓光教授，应我校科研处和生命科学学院的邀请，在生科楼</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">432</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">学术报告厅做了题为《秦岭川金丝猴行为生态学研究》的学术报告。生科院</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">60</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">余名教师、研究生聆听了报告。报告由院长张泽均教授主持。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">齐教授以幽默风趣的语言，生动地介绍了金丝猴的形态特征、社会行为、社会体系形成机制等方面的内容，赢得了在场师生的阵阵掌声。讲座结束后，师生踊跃提问，齐教授从专业角度都一一给予了耐心的解答。本次讲座增进了师生们对行为生态学研究前沿的了解，开阔了研究视野。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/Upload/image/20161115/6361481723722121122859147.png\" title=\"西北大学齐晓光教授来我校讲学.png\" alt=\"西北大学齐晓光教授来我校讲学.png\" width=\"763\" height=\"545\"/></p>', '/Upload/article/20161115/dfc52d31dd5147499f64a368f6e9ac44.png', '0', 'tzgg', '通知公告', 'zxdt', '最新动态', '10000', '3', '2016-06-06 00:00:00', '');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('8', '管理员', '', '实验室', '知名校友、福州大学水产养殖专家袁重桂博士来我校讲学', '<p style=\"text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">民以食为天，健康、安全的水产品事关人民群众的身体健康和生命安全。</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">6</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">20</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">日下午</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">3</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">：</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">30</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">，受西华师范大学生命科学学院和生态研究院的邀请，我校知名校友，著名的名、特、优水产动物养殖专家，福州大学袁重桂博士来我校讲学，在生科楼</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">432</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">学术厅作了题为《水产可控生态精养技术及其原理》的学术报告。会议由生态研究院周材权院长主持，水生生物学和动物学专业的部分老师和研究生参加了此次报告会。传统的水产业由于养殖水质、水生疾病和养殖成本等诸多问题面临发展瓶颈，袁重桂博士结合自身多年来从事中华鳖、石斑鱼、南美白对虾、鳗鲡等养殖的成功经验，从高效控制养殖条件、合理搭配混养模式、科学利用生态防御疾病机制等方面系统地阐述了可控生态水产精养殖技术的理念和标准。袁博士的可控生态水产精养殖理论告诉我们，水产养殖风险是可控的，同时水产业也可以实现零排放的环保型产业。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">报告会后袁博士还同在座的师生分享了创业的宝贵经验，勉励大家坚持梦想，把握时机，为我国水产事业做出更大的贡献。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/Upload/image/20161115/6361481739935221247924958.jpg\" title=\"知名校友、福州大学水产养殖专家袁重桂博士来我校讲学.jpg\" alt=\"知名校友、福州大学水产养殖专家袁重桂博士来我校讲学.jpg\"/></p>', '/Upload/article/20161115/9385d229d9f64d02bd26be3adffc20e6.jpg', '0', 'tzgg', '通知公告', 'zxdt', '最新动态', '10000', '3', '2016-06-21 00:00:00', '');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('9', '管理员', '', '实验室', 'Pistillody mutant reveals key insights into stamen and pistil development in wheat  (Triticum aestivum L.)', '<table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;-webkit-touch-callout:none;-webkit-user-select:none;-khtml-user-select:none;-moz-user-select:none;-ms-user-select:none;user-select:none\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr class=\"firstRow\">\n            <td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">\n                作者：\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all\">\n                <span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">Yang ZJ</span>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">\n                刊物名称：\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all\">\n                <span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">Bmc Genomics</span>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">\n                论文题目英文：\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\">\n                <span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">Pistillody mutant reveals key insights into stamen and pistil development in wheat (<em>Triticum aestivum</em> L.)</span>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">\n                年：\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\">\n                2015\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">\n                <p>\n                    卷：\n                </p>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\">\n                15\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">\n                页：\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\">\n                <span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">1-10</span>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">\n                联系作者：\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\">\n                <span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">Peng ZS</span>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">\n                影响因子：\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\">\n                <span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">3.867</span>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr style=\"height:300px\">\n            <td width=\"165\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">\n                摘要：\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\">\n                <span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">The pistillody mutant wheat (<em>Triticum aestivum</em> L.) plant HTS-1 exhibits homeotic transformation of stamens into pistils or pistil-like structures. Unlike common wheat varieties, HTS-1 produces three to six pistils per floret, potentially increasing the yield. Thus, HTS-1 is highly valuable in the study of floral development in wheat. In this study, we conducted RNA sequencing of the transcriptomes of the pistillody stamen (PS) and the pistil (P) from HTS-1 plants, and the stamen (S) from the non-pistillody control variety Chinese Spring TP to gain insights into pistil and stamen development in wheat.</span>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"2\" align=\"center\">\n                <a href=\"http://xueshu.baidu.com/s?wd=paperuri%3A%28ad55103b870d26c0641975c5a7987379%29&filter=sc_long_sign&tn=SE_xueshusource_2kduw22v&sc_vurl=http%3A%2F%2Feuropepmc.org%2Farticles%2FPMC4369888%2F&ie=utf-8&sc_us=14127041423285129332\" target=\"_self\" title=\"下载\" textvalue=\"下载\" class=\"keylab-self-a\">下载</a> <a href=\"javascript:window.opener=null;window.open(\'\',\'_self\');window.close();\" target=\"_self\" title=\"关闭窗口\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#000;margin-left:100px\">关闭窗口</a> <a href=\"/index/index\" target=\"_self\" title=\"返回主页\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#000;margin-left:100px\">返回主页</a>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n    <br/>\n</p>', '', '0', 'xsky', '学术科研', 'kycg', '最新科研成功', '10000', '3', '2016-11-15 00:00:00', '');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('10', '管理员', '', '实验室', '廖文波研究员课题组在两栖动物脑形态大小进化机理研究上的最新进展', '<p style=\"text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">脑是中枢神经系统的重要组成部分，位于颅腔内。动物脑的高级功能就是学习和认知。对兽类和灵长类脑形态结构的研究表明，脑形态大小与认知密切相关。关于脑</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">形态大小的进化有两种假说：认知假说和能量代价假说。通常情况下，动物发育更大的脑是为了增加识别食物和天敌的能力，这是认知假说；然而在不利的环境条件</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">下，动物也可以改变策略，将发育供给脑的部分能量投入其他器官，这就是能量代价假说。基于以上假说，本课题组以</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">种两栖动物为模式动物，验证了两栖动物</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">脑形态大小的进化特征。结果发现，两栖动物脑形态大小进化与环境因子密切相关，脑形态大小的变化与消化道发达程度呈显著性负相关，研究结果支持能量代价假</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">说。此外本研究还发现性选择对脑形态大小进化的影响不显著。本研究成果</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">“Large brains, small guts: The expensive tissue hypothesis supported within anurans”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">“Sexual selection impacts brain anatomy in frogs and toads”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分别发表在国际权威刊物《</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">The American Naturalist</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》和《</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Ecology and Evolution</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》上。</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\"><br/> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">本课题由西华师范大学廖文波研究员、娄尚灵同学、曾燏博士和瑞典斯德哥尔摩大学</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Kotrschal</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">博士共同完成，廖文波研究员为论文的通讯作者。本课题是在国家自然科学基金和四川省杰出青年基金资助下完成的。</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\"><br/> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">近来年，该课题组在两栖动物脑形态大小方面的研究成果相继发表在国际期刊《</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Journal of Evolutionary Biology</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、《</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Evolutionary Biology</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》、《</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Herpetological Journal</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》和《</span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">Acta Herpetologica</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》上，这些研究为两栖动物脑大小进化机理提供了理论基础。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '', '0', 'tzgg', '通知公告', 'zxdt', '最新动态', '10000', '3', '2016-07-30 00:00:00', '');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('11', '管理员', '', '实验室', '四川省昆虫学学会会员代表大会在我校召开', '<p style=\"text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">8</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">28</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">日，由四川省昆虫学学会主办、西华师范大学承办的四川省昆虫学学会会员代表大会在我校华凤校区图书馆</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">306</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">会议室隆重召开。中国科学院院士、中科院动物研究所所长、中国昆虫学会理事长康乐研究员，中国科学院动物研究所副所长、中国兽类学会理事长魏辅文研究员，四川省民政厅行政审批处副处长安亮，四川蚕业研究所所长肖金树研究员，四川植保学会副理事长李庆教授，我校副校长李健教授，科研处处长刘进教授，生科院院长张泽钧教授，著名的隐翅虫专家郑发科教授以及来自四川省各高校和科研机构的</span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;\">120</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">余名代表参加了会议。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">会议开幕式由张泽钧院长主持。四川省民政厅行政审批处安亮副处长宣读了四川省昆虫学学会成立通知书。副校长李健致欢迎辞。他代表学校向会议的顺利召开表示祝贺，对与会专家、代表表示热烈欢迎，并简要介绍了学校和生科院的发展情况。他表示，四川省昆虫学学会的成立，必将对我省昆虫学研究事业的普及与发展起到极大的促进作用。此次大会在我校召开，既是各位专家、代表对我校昆虫学研究领域所取得的成绩的肯定，更是对我校的信任与支持。他承诺，学校将以最大的决心，尽最大的努力，为学会的繁荣发展和四川省昆虫学研究事业做出新的更大的贡献。康乐院士代表中国昆虫学会向大会的顺利召开表示祝贺，并简要回顾了中国昆虫学学会成立的历史，他表示，四川昆虫学的发展对中国昆虫学的研究具有重要意义，他期望四川省昆虫学研究者能为中国昆虫学事业的发展贡献更多的力量。中国兽类学会理事长魏辅文研究员在致词中强调，昆虫学研究在整个动物学研究领域具有十分重要的地位。四川蚕业研究所所长肖金树研究员和四川植保学会副理事长李庆教授也分别致词，向昆虫学学会的成立表示祝贺。重庆市昆虫学学会、四川省大熊猫生态与文化建设促进会分别发来贺词，向大会的胜利召开表示祝贺！</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">开幕式结束后，与</span> <span style=\";font-family:宋体\">会代表审议通过了《四川省昆虫学学会章程》，并选举产生了首届理事和理事会。我校生科院石爱民教授被选为理事长、张烈教授被选为副理事长、何恒果博士被选</span> <span style=\";font-family:宋体\">为秘书长。此后，中科院康乐院士、我校生科院石爱民教授以及四川农业大学、四川省农科院植保所、乐山师范学院、达州市植保植检站等单位的专家、学者作了精彩的学术报告。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\";font-family: 宋体\">本次会议的成功召开，对提高四川省昆虫学研究水平、促进昆虫学研究人才培养等方面起到了积极作用，同时也为四川省昆虫学工作者搭建了一个交流与合作的平台。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/Upload/image/20161115/6361481761152614218138817.jpg\" title=\"四川省昆虫学学会会员代表大会在我校召开.jpg\" alt=\"四川省昆虫学学会会员代表大会在我校召开.jpg\"/></p>', '/Upload/article/20161115/7c44add7ac8c46c1a7ea5382bc80e9b6.jpg', '120', 'tzgg', '通知公告', 'zxdt', '最新动态', '10000', '3', '2016-08-30 00:00:00', '');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('12', '管理员', '', '实验室', 'Salt stress induced sex-related spatial heterogeneity of gas exchange rates over the leaf surface in Populus cathayana Rehd', '<table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;-webkit-touch-callout:none;-webkit-user-select:none;-khtml-user-select:none;-moz-user-select:none;-ms-user-select:none;user-select:none\"><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">作者：</td><td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">Xu X</span></td></tr><tr><td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">刊物名称：</td><td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">Acta Physiologiae Plantarum</span></td></tr><tr><td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">论文题目英文：</td><td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">Salt stress induced sex-related spatial heterogeneity of gas exchange rates over the leaf surface in <em>Populus cathayana </em>Rehd</span></td></tr><tr><td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">年：</td><td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\">2015</td></tr><tr><td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\"><p>卷：</p></td><td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\">37</td></tr><tr><td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">页：</td><td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\">1-10</td></tr><tr><td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">联系作者：</td><td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">Xu X</span></td></tr><tr><td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">影响因子：</td><td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">1.563</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height:300px\"><td width=\"165\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">摘要：</td><td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">The sex-related spatial heterogeneity of gas exchange rates over the leaf surface under salt stress was investigated in the dioecious species, Populus cathayana Rehd. Cuttings were subjected to two salt regimes: 0 and 75 mM NaCl added to the Hoagland solution, the control and the treatment group, respectively. Measurements of gas exchange parameters were taken from over 40 sites on the surfaces of representative ‘non-stressed’ and ‘salt-treated’ leaves which had the same insertion point for two sexual cuttings. Compared to the control group, the treatment group showed a significant decrease in the mean values of the following: water use efficiency (WUE), Chlorophyll a (Chl <em>a</em>) concentration, chlorophyll b (Chl <em>b</em>) concentration, concentration of carotenoids (Caro), total chlorophyll concentration (TC) in two sexes, and net photosynthesis rate (<em>P<sub>n</sub></em>), stomatal conductance (<em>g<sub>s</sub></em>), and stomatal length/width ratio (SR) in females. Also, in the treatment group, females exhibited lower WUE, <em>P<sub>n</sub></em>, <em>g<sub>s</sub></em>, <em>E</em>, Chl <em>a</em>, Chl <em>b</em>, TC, and SR than males. Comparison of contour maps showed that the net photosynthesis rate decreased gradually from apical to basal zones over the leaf surface occurred in the two sexes under natural conditions, but under salt stress, the opposite trend was found in females only. The results suggest that the heterogeneity pattern of the gas exchange parameters in response to salt stress between the two sexes is quite different due to different strategies employed by males and females to maintain the photosynthesis rate under salt stress. This heterogeneity phenomenon under salt stress may mainly be attributed to the chlorophyll pigments in males and the stomatal apertures in females.</span></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://xueshu.baidu.com/s?wd=paperuri%3A%288ee44e16fe019cc92e17f019f432a4f2%29&filter=sc_long_sign&tn=SE_xueshusource_2kduw22v&sc_vurl=http%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2F10.1007%2Fs11738-014-1709-3&ie=utf-8&sc_us=14272548303462595864\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"下载\" textvalue=\"下载\" class=\"keylab-self-a\">下载</a> <a href=\"javascript:window.opener=null;window.open(\'\',\'_self\');window.close();\" target=\"_self\" title=\"关闭窗口\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#000;margin-left:100px\">关闭窗口</a> <a href=\"/index/index\" target=\"_self\" title=\"返回主页\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#000;margin-left:100px\">返回主页</a></td></tr></tbody></table><p><br/></p>', '', '0', 'xsky', '学术科研', 'kycg', '最新科研成功', '10000', '3', '2016-11-15 00:00:00', '');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('13', '管理员', '', '实验室', 'Female-biased sexual size dimorphism is driven by phenotypic selection on females  in the Omei treefrog', '<table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;-webkit-touch-callout:none;-webkit-user-select:none;-khtml-user-select:none;-moz-user-select:none;-ms-user-select:none;user-select:none\"><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">作者：</td><td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">Ma XH</span></td></tr><tr><td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">刊物名称：</td><td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">Herpetological Journal</span></td></tr><tr><td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">论文题目英文：</td><td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">Female-biased sexual size dimorphism is driven by phenotypic selection on females in the Omei treefrog.</span></td></tr><tr><td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">年：</td><td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\">2015</td></tr><tr><td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\"><p>卷：</p></td><td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\">25</td></tr><tr><td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">页：</td><td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">123-125</span></td></tr><tr><td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">联系作者：</td><td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">Liao WB</span></td></tr><tr><td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">影响因子：</td><td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">0.808</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height:300px\"><td width=\"165\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" align=\"right\">摘要：</td><td width=\"802\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">Sexual size dimorphism (SSD) is a widespread phenomenon commonly attributed to sex-specific patterns of selection on body size. Using data from Dengchigou population of the Omei treefrog (Rhacophorus omeimontis) in Fengtongzhai National Nature Reserve, southwestern China, we evaluated the hypothesis that direct phenotypic selection on both males and females can produce SSD. Female biased-SSD was generally driven by selection on females due to fecundity advantage of large body size rather than sexual selection favouring large male body size. Furthermore, differences in life-history traits (i.e. growth rate and/or time available for growth) between the sexes also resulted in female biased-SSD. Our findings suggest that the relationship between female size and fecundity supports the prediction that selection for fecundity drives female biased-SSD.</span></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-style:solid;word-break:break-all;background-color:#99e299\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://xueshu.baidu.com/s?wd=paperuri%3A%28c3df7f7810d4d7afffb48d036e80f2e8%29&filter=sc_long_sign&tn=SE_xueshusource_2kduw22v&sc_vurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ingentaconnect.com%2Fcontent%2Fbhs%2Fthj%2F2015%2F00000025%2F00000002%2Fart00007&ie=utf-8&sc_us=3016526185395085268\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"下载\" textvalue=\"下载\" class=\"keylab-self-a\">下载</a> <a href=\"javascript:window.opener=null;window.open(\'\',\'_self\');window.close();\" target=\"_self\" title=\"关闭窗口\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#000;margin-left:100px\">关闭窗口</a> <a href=\"/index/index\" target=\"_self\" title=\"返回主页\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#000;margin-left:100px\">返回主页</a></td></tr></tbody></table><p><br/></p>', '', '0', 'xsky', '学术科研', 'kycg', '最新科研成功', '10000', '3', '2016-11-16 00:00:00', '');

